headline: Jim Cramer Considers Jabil One of His Favorites
summary: Jabil Inc. (NYSE:JBL) is one of the stocks Jim Cramer put under the microscope. Cramer called it one of his favorites, as he commented: “Right now, we’ve got a quiet bull market in what’s called contract manufacturers, although they do far more than that, the companies that provide outsourced manufacturing for all sorts of industries.
